 optimized data and battery experience, please go to https://www.brave.com<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Note:</span>&nbsp;Brave for Android is Brave\'s tab-based browser and is different from Brave Browser - Link Bubble, which loads pages in the background.<br><br><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Support:</span>&nbsp;If you have any questions, please feel free to reach out to us at support@brave.com</p></div></div><div class=\"additional\" dt-eid=\"card\" dt-params=\"model_type=1027&amp;module_name=&amp;position=4\" dt-clck-ignore=\"true\" dt-imp-once=\"true\" dt-imp-end-ignore=\"true\" dt-send-beacon=\"true\" style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); margin-top: 20px; position: relative; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><h3 class=\" google-anno-skip \" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 64, 67); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 24px;\">Additional APP Information</h3><div class=\"additional-content\" style=\"border-color: rgb(231, 231, 231); border-top-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 12px;\"><div class=\"additional-item\" style=\"border-color: rgb(231, 231, 231); border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; height: 56px; line-height: 22px; padding: 8px 12px; width: 417.6px;\"><p class=\"title\" style=\"margin-top: -1px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(94, 94, 94); overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\">Latest Version</p><p class=\"additional-info\" style=\"padding: 0px; color: rgb(139, 139, 139); font-size: 12px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\"><a class=\"requestupdate ga\" title=\"Request Brave Update\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://apkpure.com/need-update.html?pkg=com.brave.browser\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 166, 237); text-decoration: none;\"><img width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"req_update\" alt=\"Request Brave Update\" src=\"https://static.apkpur